OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA cloudy
OL,6,Fevening with light outbreaks of rain
OL,7,Ffor Orkney, Shetland staying dry.
OL,8,FRemaining cloudy overnight with rain
OL,9,Fbecoming heavier and more persistent
OL,10,Ffor Orkney, some light rain possible
OL,11,Ffor southern Shetland for a time.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FOrkney cloudy with rain at
OL,14,Ftimes, some heavy, breezy later.
OL,15,FShetland starting dry with some
OL,16,Fsunshine then clouding over with some
OL,17,Frain in the afternoon, lighter winds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
