OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FA
OL,6,Fmixed few days which will be mostly
OL,7,Fcloudy with outbreaks of rain at times
OL,8,Fbut still a few dry and bright or
OL,9,Fsunny spells. Winds mostly light.
